PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Supply and Services of JANICE COCHRANE, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation from the public service of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Dan E.
